	<div class="broad-matter">
		<div class="broad-detail">
			<h2 class="castTitle">分三等奖发顺丰哈迪</h2>
			<p class="castBody">发大水了公开独守空房了独守空房发送的酸辣公开独守空房了独守空房发送的酸辣jgjgh gdfgfdgd的酸辣公开独守空房了独守空房发送的酸辣的</p>			
		</div>
		<div class="check-datails">查看详情</div>
	</div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
	$(".overview").click(function() {
		$(".broadcast .castTitle").html($(".title").val() || "请填写标题");
		$(".broadcast .castBody").html($(".content").val() || "请填写广播内容");
		$(".broadcast").show();
	});
	$(".broadcast .broad-head span").click(function() {
		$(".broadcast").hide();
	});
</script>